fact WorkItem(
  id: "WI-156",
  description: "scaland resync — expression evaluator (proposal 026 / 026.1). Port the Rust eval/ subsystem to Scala: closures, pattern matching, evaluation frames, value arena, effects. ~10 source files in rustland/anthill-core/src/eval/ — the largest single deferred item; estimated multi-week effort. Read proposals 026 + 026.1 + design notes in docs/proposals/ before writing code; design the Scala value/closure representation up front (whether to use Scala native lambdas as the Closure type, or a frame-based interpreter mirroring rust's Frame/Value arenas). Acceptance: sbt test green; eval-test parity with rustland/anthill-core/tests/eval_*.rs on the agreed core fragment (literals → field access → let → match → lambda → effect-tagged operations).",
